<1ST_LINE>r p AM-PP-Pres-TotVot-Sum     03-23 0190</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-PP-Pres-TotVot-Sum,190</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>3-23-88</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   Here is the current breakdown of all the votes cast in the
primaries so far. For each candidate the total is calculated by
adding together the votes the candidate received in each of the
primaries.
</TEXT>
<HEAD>DEMOCRATIC</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   61,828 of 62,100 precincts reporting -  99.6 percent
   
   Dukakis, 2,953,568 -  25.6 percent
