<HEAD>10 To Be Hanged For Political Murders</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DHAKA, Bangladesh (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A judge sentenced 10 people to death by
hanging for murdering a left-wing politician and his son three
years ago, news reports said Wednesday.
   Judge Kazi Golam Rasul passed the sentence at Narail, 60 miles
west of Dhaka, on Tuesday.
   The convicts, who will be hanged unless they appeal to higher
