<TEXT>
   A general strike aimed at ousting
Gen. Manuel Antonio Noriega closed shops nationwide, but food was
running low and Noriega again rejected a U.S. call for him to
surrender power and go into exile.
   ``I am a Panamanian not a gringo,'' Noriega said after meeting
