Foreigner,'' about the limits of friendship. Helen Hayes, 944-9450.
Teletron. Ticketron. Available. Closes April 9.
   _ ``The Phantom of the Opera,'' the lavish Andrew Lloyd Webber
musical about a deformed composer who haunts the Paris Opera House
and the young soprano he loves. Majestic, 239-6290, same number as
Telecharge. Difficult.
